 l.5 δ</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Αὐρήλιος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Αὐρήλιος\">Αὐρήλιος</span>  <span data-text=\"Ῥεστοῦτος\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ῥεστοῦτος\">Ῥεστοῦτος</span>  <span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"καί\">καὶ</span>  <span data-text=\"Ζωσίμη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Ζωσίμη\">Ζωσίμη</span>  <span data-text=\"ἠγοράσομεν\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἀγοράζω\">ἠγοράσομεν</span>  <span data-text=\"ἐκ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ἐκ\">ἐκ</span>  <span data-text=\"τῶν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">τῶν</span>  <span data-text=\"ἰδείων\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἴδιος\">ἰδείων</span>  <span data-text=\"ἡμῖν\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἡμεῖς\">ἡμῖν</span>  <span data-text=\"τὴν\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">τὴν</span>  <span data-text=\"ἒνβασιν\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"ἔμβασις\">ἒνβασιν</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[..]<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ΑΛὐρήλι\n                    ος Ῥεστοῦτος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ΑΛὐρήλι\n                    ος\"><span data-text=\"ΑΛὐρήλι\n                    ος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Αὐρήλιος\">ΛΥΡΗΛΙ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[.]Σ</span></span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ῥεστοῦτος\"><span data-text=\"Ῥεστοῦτος\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ῥεστοῦτος\">ΡΕΣΤΟΥΤΟΣ</span></span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"καί\">ΚΑΙ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ζωσίμη\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζωσίμη\"><span data-text=\"Ζωσίμη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Ζωσίμη\">ΖΩΣΙΜΗ</span></span></span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ἠγοράσομεν\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἀγοράζω\">ΗΓΟΡΑΣΟΜΕΝ</span><br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"ἐκ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ἐκ\">[.]Κ</span><span data-text=\"τῶν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">ΤΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἰδγείων\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἴδιος\">ΙΓΕΙΩΝ</span><br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span><span data-text=\"ἡμῖν\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἡμεῖς\">[....</span><span data-text=\"τὴν\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">..]Ν</span><span data-text=\"ἒνβασιν\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"ἔμβασις\">ΕΝΒΑΣΙΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\">l.1 Α | l.5 δ</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Αὐρήλιος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Αὐρήλιος\">ΑΥΡΗΛΙΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"Ῥεστοῦτος\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ῥεστοῦτος\">ΡΕΣΤΟΥΤΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"καί\">ΚΑΙ</span><span data-text=\"Ζωσίμη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Ζωσίμη\">ΖΩΣΙΜΗ</span><span data-text=\"ἠγοράσομεν\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἀγοράζω\">ΗΓΟΡΑΣΟΜΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἐκ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ἐκ\">ΕΚ</span><span data-text=\"τῶν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">ΤΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἰδείων\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἴδιος\">ΙΔΕΙΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἡμῖν\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἡμεῖς\">ΗΜΙΝ</span><span data-text=\"τὴν\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">ΤΗΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἒνβασιν\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"ἔμβασις\">ΕΝΒΑΣΙΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001348_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001348_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001348.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001348-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text based on photographs</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"1\">1: <span>Ferrua, Korhonen: ((Chi-rho)); Kaibel: Μ(ᾶρκος)</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"2\">2: <span>Franz: Ῥεστ[ιτ]οῦτος</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"4\">4: <span>Franz: ἠγοράσαμεν; Kaibel, Wessel, Korhonen: ἠγοράσομεν (“mixto imperfecto et aoristo ortum” Kaibel, see also IG 14.96)</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"5\">5: <span> Franz: ἰίων; Kaibel, Wessel, Korhonen: ἰ είων </span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"6\">6: <span> Franz:ν βάσιν; Kaibel suggested in apparatus ἐν πᾶκι? and Wessel ἐν .ac (see also ἐν πάκης in IGCVO 602); Ferrua [ἠμι]ν ἔνβασιν; Korhonen [ἠμι]ν [?] ἔνβασιν (but also τὴ]ν is possible) </span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo</a></p>  <p>((Chi-Rho)) Aurelios Rhestoutos and Zosime, we purchased this tomb at our expense.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo</a></p>  <p>((Chi-Rho)) Aurelios Rhestoutos e Zosime, acquistammo questa tomba a nostre spese.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>This is a marble plaque and not a sarcophagus, which must have served to mark a “loculus”, according to the interpretation that J. and L. Robert (BE 1964 nr. 631) gave for a similar inscription from Catania, RAC 8 (1931) 122-25 = <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001547\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001547</a>. This inscription attests to the purchase of the tomb by the deceased who are buried in it: the names of the deceased are followed by the verb <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἀγοράω</span>, an expression indicating that the purchase was made at their own expense (<span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἐκ τῶν ἰδίων</span>) and by the object (for <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἔνβασις</span> as the tomb, see AE 1996.0792 = <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001423\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001423</a> and Ferrua 1958: 172). It is possible that there was a reflexive pronoun in the lacuna of l. 6, as in other cases where the deceased purchased the grave for himself: IMusCatania 229 = <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001628\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001628</a>. For the registration of the purchase of the tomb in Christian epitaphs, see Führer and Schultze (1907: 12-15) and Korhonen (2004: 108-110). The cognomen of the deceased must have been Restitutus but for such a form, see ICUR 19782. The name of the woman, <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Ζωσίμη</span>, is attested in other inscriptions of the city (CIL 10.7016 = <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000300\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000300</a>, IMusCatania 165 = <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001649\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001649</a>) and more in general of Sicily (LGPN 3A: 190).</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 856 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394</a>  </li><li> Amico 1741 259 no.15 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1769 166 no.19 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1784 173 no.19 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083</a>  </li><li> Ferrara 1829 349 no.1 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005</a>  </li><li> Franz 1853 5723 with p.1250 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">529</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Ferrua 1989 no.437 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995</a>  </li><li> Korhonen 2004 176 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li> 1964.0631 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282</a> Ferrua 1958 172 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001998\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001998</a> Führer and Schultze 1907 12-15 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001979\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001979</a>  </li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Irregular letters: lunate Ε and Σ; cursive Μ and Ω; Α and Λ with extended serifs.</p> Lines 1-6  10-25  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
